# TOOLS.md - LinkedIn Agent

## Local Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| schedule.json | Daily tasks with jitter. Read every heartbeat. |
| limits.json | Source of truth for counts. Increment after actions. |
| queries.json | Search queries by topic. Generated daily by content planner. |
| memory/{date}.md | Append-only log. Types: Heartbeat, Comment, Reply, Reaction, Post/Article/Poll/Repost/Newsletter, Connection Request, Error |

## Browser

`profile: "{{browser_profile}}"` on EVERY call. No API — 100% browser.

URLs: Feed `/feed/`, Notifications `/notifications/`, Profile `/in/{{handle_slug}}`, Search `/search/results/content/`

## Post Quality Filter

1. Fresh (24-48h), 10+ reactions, relevant ({{#each pillars}}{{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}})
2. Not crowded (<100 comments, 5-30 ideal)
3. Like first (mandatory)
4. ALWAYS `datePosted="past-week"` in search (NOT past-24h)

## Content Strategies

### Posts
See POST-TEMPLATES.md. Pick unused template, self-review (SOUL.md), peak hours (15:00-17:00 Kyiv). 3-5 hashtags (read from `queries.json → hashtags` array — refreshed daily).

### Articles
1000-2000 words, personal story. "{{role}} by day, builder by night." Topics drawn from pillars: {{#each pillars}}{{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}.{{#if conferences_text}} Conference insights from {{conferences_text}}.{{/if}} Tuesday + Friday (mandatory). End with question.

### Polls
4 options (1 funny). No product in poll — only in follow-up comment. See BROWSER-post.md SS 9.

### Newsletter
"Weekend Builder" — Monday AM. Hook → Updates → Lesson → CTA.

### Repost
Browse feed (NOT search). 2-4 sentences commentary. Self-review.

## Connection Requests

Auto-send after commenting. Safety checks → BROWSER-notifications.md SS 7 (profile → custom-invite → personalized note → send). Skip if: recruiter headline, already pending/connected, Creator Mode.

## Engagement Windows (Kyiv)

- **15:00-17:00** BEST (8-10am US East)
- **19:00-20:00** good
- **10:00-11:00** decent

## Schedule Templates

4 engagement windows daily (~10:00, 13:00, 15:00, 19:00). Mon=Newsletter + 4 engage. Tue/Fri=Article + 3 engage. Wed=4 engage. Thu=Poll/Post + 4 engage. Sat=3 engage. Sun=1 engage.

End-of-day (every day): update_memory ~22:00.

Capacity: Σ comments = daily.comments.limit, Σ reactions = daily.reactions.limit. Ramp weekly per limits.json ramp_plan.
